aircrack-ng  itself is  a  802.11  WEP  / WPA-PSK key cracker. 
It implements the so-called Fluhrer - Mantin -  Shamir  (FMS)
attack,  along  with some new attacks by a talented hacker na-
med KoreK. 

aircrack-ng suite also includes the following tools:

* airdecap-ng decrypts a WEP/WPA crypted pcap file.
* ivstools  extract  ivs  from a pcap file or merges several
  ivs files into one.
* kstats  shows  statistical  FMS algorithm votes for an ivs
  dump and a specified WEP key.
